(81, 1, '2023-07-13 16:24:14', '2023-07-13 16:24:14', 'Thng tin sn phm mt ong rng ca Nng Sn Sch\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Ngun gc xut x</td>\r\n<td>Huyn Tr My / Tin Phc, tnh Qung Nam</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Cht lng</td>\r\n<td>Mt ong rng t nhin, sn xut th cng, nguyn cht 100%</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>ng chai</td>\r\n<td>Chai thy tinh 1000ml (2 chai loi 500ml)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>S dng</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>n trc tip, trn vi kem sa, pht ln bnh m, pha tr, nc cam, chanh, pha ru,</li>\r\n 	<li>Ngm tam tht, bt ngh, phn hoa</li>\r\n 	<li>Ch bin thc phm, lm bnh ko, quay g, vt</li>\r\n 	<li>Mt ong l cht ngt t nhin, giu vitamin v khong cht nn lng dng ty theo s thch, khng gy phn ng ph</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\nQung Nam  vng t ni ting  nc ta vi cc mn c sn c bit v c o khin ai cng mun n y  th mt ln. Mt s thc phm cng dng c bit tt cho sc khe ch c  Qung Nam k n nh:<strong>nm lim xanh</strong>,<strong>sm ngc linh</strong>,<strong>tiu ngun Tin Phc</strong> c bit mt loi mt ong<strong>c sn Qung Nam</strong>m khng th khng nhc ti  l<strong>mt ong rng</strong>Tr My / Tin Phc  y l sn phm hin ang rt c a chung s dng.\r\n<h2 id=\"dac-diem-cua-mat-ong-rung-nguyen-chat\"><strong>C IM CA MT ONG RNG NGUYN CHT</strong></h2>\r\n<strong>Mt ong rng</strong> Tr My / Tin Phc  Qung Nam khng h c s tc ng ca con ngi v hon ton t nhin, mt ong rng thng c thu hoch duy nht trong 1 ma tm khong t thng 3 ti thng 6 mi nm, mt ong rng mang m v c trng ca cc bng hoa rng, c v ngt v thanh.<strong>Mt ong rng nguyn cht</strong>c mu rt a dng, t nu sm ti vng sm,  kt dnh tng i cao.\r\n<h2 id=\"tac-dung-cua-mat-ong-rung\"><strong>TC DNG CA MT ONG RNG</strong></h2>\r\n<strong>Mt ong rng</strong>khng phi t nhin m c mi ngi a chung s dng. N va l c sn ni ting, va mang li rt nhiu tc dng hiu qu cho sc khe con ngi. C th k ti mt s<strong>tc dng ca mt ong rng</strong>nh:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Tng cng sc  khng c th cho ngi ln tui, tr em, ph n mang thai, ngi mi m dy v gip cho thn hnh lun khe mnh.</li>\r\n 	<li>Tng cng sinh lc, gip sc khe c bi b, h tr phng nga tt cc bnh v h h hp, vim hng, ho lao, tiu ng, tim mch, vim i trang, vim lot d dy, c th b suy nhc</li>\r\n 	<li>C cng dng lm mn, gi m v p da.</li>\r\n 	<li>S dng trc mi ba n s gip nga tnh trng bo ph</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nTham kho mua<strong>tinh bt ngh</strong>nguyn cht<strong>ti y</strong>\r\n<h2 id=\"phan-biet-mat-ong-rung-nguyen-chat-va-mat-ong-nuoi\"><strong>PHN BIT MT ONG RNG NGUYN CHT V MT ONG NUI</strong></h2>\r\n<h3 id=\"phan-biet-bang-cach-nem-thu\"><strong>PHN BIT BNG CCH NM TH</strong></h3>\r\nDo<strong>mt ong rng</strong>c ngun tc xut pht t t nhin nn v n ngt thanh v khng ngt th nh mt ong nui. Mt ong rng c mi thm cc k c trng, y l mi hng c to thnh t rt nhiu loi hoa rng khc nhau.\r\n<h3 id=\"phan-biet-bang-cach-quan-sat\"><strong>PHN BIT BNG CCH QUAN ST</strong></h3>\r\nTrong thi tit nng th mt ong rng thng xut hin nhiu bt v kh gas. Cc loi mt ong bnh thng khc th t bt v t to kh hn, thm ch l vi c mt ong nui cng t to kh v bt. Ngoi ra, mt ong nui c hn nhiu so vi mt ong rng.\r\n\r\n<em>Mt ong rng Tr My nguyn cht xn 100%</em>\r\n<h2 id=\"bao-quan-mat-ong-rung\"><strong>BO QUN MT ONG RNG</strong></h2>\r\nSau khi khai thc<strong>mt ong rng</strong>th thi gian dng tm khong 2 nm vi loi mt ong gia ma v u ma (loi ny c mu vng cam, vng chanh), thi gian dng 3 nm vi loi mt ong cui ma (loi ny mu en sm)\r\n<h3 id=\"tai-sao-bao-quan-mat-ong-rung-dau-va-giua-mua-lai-khac-cuoi-mua\"><strong>TI SAO BO QUN MT ONG RNG U V GIA MA LI KHC CUI MA?</strong></h3>\r\nC mt s chnh lch v thi gian s dng gia mt ong cui mua v u ma, bn c bit nguyn nhn ti sao khng? L do l ti t mt ong gia v u ma thng ln 1 t phn hoa v nhng non lm y nhanh qu trnh ln men khin mt ong nhanh b chua. Cn vi mt ong rng vo cui ma th  c lu hn do nhng lc ny  thnh ong th, cn phn hoa th b ong n ht nn qu trinh ln men khng b kch thch. V mt l thuyt th khi khai thc sp ong s cn phi loi b ht ong gia, nhng non v phn hoa. Tuy nhin thc t th rt kh  loi c 100% nhng thnh phn ny, v th ch nn dng v bo qun<strong>mt ong rng</strong>nh hng dn bn trn  mang li hiu qu ti a.\r\n<h3 id=\"luu-y-khi-bao-quan-mat-ong-rung-nguyen-sap\"><strong>LU  KHI BO QUN MT ONG RNG NGUYN SP</strong></h3>\r\ni vi<strong>mt ong rng nguyn cht</strong>con nguyn sp th c mt s ch  nh sau y: chi nn  ti a khong 5-6 thng k t ngy ly. Sau khong thi gian ny, bn phi vt ri tch ring mt khi sp. Khng nn  lu v nu  lu sp s b ln phn hoa, nhng non, kch thch qu trinh ln men lm hng mt.\r\n<h2 id=\"gia-mat-ong-rung-hien-nay-la-bao-nhieu-tai-ha-noi-va-ho-chi-minh\"><strong>GI MT ONG RNG HIN NAY L BAO NHIU TIH NI V H CH MINH?</strong></h2>\r\nNh phn ni dung   cp pha trn, mt ong rng va rt tt cho sc khe, va c ngun gc t t nhin l s lng mi nm khng nhiu. Ngoi ra, do nh cu mua mt ong rng ngy cng tng nn gi ca n tng i cao. Hin ti<strong>gi mt ong rng</strong>nguyn cht ca Nng Sn Sch ang vo khong<strong>1.200.000/chai 1000ml.</strong><strong>u i ch cn 1.000.000/chai 1000ml khi t hng trc tuyn ti website</strong>\r\n<h2 id=\"o-dau-ban-mat-ong-rung-nguyen-chat-tai-ha-noi-va-ho-chi-minh\"><strong> U BN MT ONG RNG NGUYN CHT TIH NI V H CH MINH?</strong></h2>\r\n<strong>Mt ong rng nguyn cht</strong>thng c mua trc tip t ngi dn hoc c cung cp bi 1 s c s thu mua lu nm ti cc tnh thnh. Gi mt ong rng nhn chung th cao hn so vi mt bng. Chnh v th m nhiu ni ch tp trung vo li nhun m lm mt ong rng gi, km cht lng. Do  <strong>mua c mt ong rng nguyn cht</strong>chun bn nn tm ti cc a ch<strong>bn mt ong rng</strong>lu nm, c ngun gc r rng v<strong>gi mt ong rng</strong>hp l.\r\n\r\nNng Sn Sch GIA LINH l mt trong nhng a ch cung cp mt ong rng uy tn. Chng ti thu mua sn phm mt ong rng trc tip t hp tc x, ngi dn i tm mt ti huyn Tr My / Tin Phc, tnh Qung Nam.\r\n\r\nXem thm:<strong>nm lim xanh</strong>,<strong>sm ngc linh</strong>Hotline:<strong>0945.414.515</strong>Mua mt ong rng ti Nng Sn Sch GIA LINH', 'Mt ong rng nguyn cht 100% t nhin', 'Mt Ong Rng nguyn cht xn 100% l phi i tm &amp; tro khai thc t cc t Ong Khoi 