(108, 1, '2023-07-14 06:52:45', '2023-07-14 06:52:45', '<p data-cursor=\"-color-purple\"><strong data-cursor=\"-color-purple\">Nm lim xanh Qung Nam</strong>l tho dc qu him ch mc ln  gc hoc thn nhng cy lim  cht trong cc khu rng nguyn sinh. S hu nhiu nguyn t vi lng cng hn 100 loi dc cht t nhin, y l mt hng<strong data-cursor=\"-color-purple\">c sn Qung Nam</strong>c cng dng vt tri i vi sc khe, c rt nhiu ngi tm mua.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 data-cursor=\"-color-green\"><span id=\"1_tim_hieu_ve_nam_lim_xanh_quang_nam\" data-cursor=\"-color-green\">1. TM HIU V NM LIM XANH QUNG NAM</span></h2>\r\n<h3 data-cursor=\"-color-green\"><span id=\"11_nam_lim_xanh_la_gi\" data-cursor=\"-color-green\">1.1. NM LIM XANH L G?</span></h3>\r\n<p data-cursor=\"-color-purple\">Nm lim xanh c tn khoa hc l Ganoderma lucidum, thuc h Nm Lim (Ganodermataceae). Loi nm ny thuc dng linh chi c hu, ch sinh trng c trong cc cnh rng nguyn sinh,  gc hoc thn nhng cy lim xanh  cht.</p>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-113 size-large\" src=\"http://localhost/wp_organic/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/nam-lim-xanh-quang-nam-1-1-1024x682.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\" data-cursor=\"-color-purple\">Nm lim xanh Qung Nam c ngun gc  vng Tin Phc (nh: Su tm)</p>\r\n<p data-cursor=\"-color-purple\">Ngun gc ca nm lim xanh Qung Nam l  vng Tin Phc. Hin nay chng cn c tm thy phn b trong rng Trng Sn, Ty Nguyn v khu vc Nam Lo. Tuy nhin, nhng cy nm lim xanh Tin Phc Qung Nam c cha nhiu dc cht qu hn cc vng khc do iu kin kh hu v th nhng ni y l l tng nht cho loi nm ny pht trin.</p>\r\n<p data-cursor=\"-color-purple\">Nm lim xanh rng Qung Nam t nhin c 2 loi: mc  gc cy lim v mc  thn cy lim. Trong , loi nm mc  gc c r mu , v ng, c m tn trng ging cy d, chn nm di ngn hoc to nh ty cy, c dc tnh cao c dng  khc phc bnh; cn loi mc  thn c hnh cnh qut, khng c chn, t c v ng, v c dng nhiu  phng nga bnh.</p>\r\n<p data-cursor=\"-color-purple\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-114\" src=\"http://localhost/wp_organic/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/nam-lim-xanh-quang-nam-2.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"476\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\" data-cursor=\"-color-purple\">Loi nm lim xanh rng t nhin  Qung Nam mc  thn cy lim (nh: Su tm)</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 data-cursor=\"-color-green\"><span id=\"12_cong_dung_cua_nam_lim_xanh_quang_nam\" data-cursor=\"-color-green\">1.2. CNG DNG CA NM LIM XANH QUNG NAM</span></h3>\r\n<p data-cursor=\"-color-purple\">T khong hn 2000 nm trc, nm lim xanh  l loi tho dc qu him c s dng trong ng Y, c tnh bnh, v ng, dng  iu tr nhiu bnh l, thm ch c cc bnh nan y.</p>\r\n<p data-cursor=\"-color-purple\">Trong y hc hin i, nm lim xanh Qung Nam c chng minh l c cha hn 100 loi dc cht qu, trong  ng ch  nht l cc loi sau:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li aria-level=\"1\"><strong data-cursor=\"-color-purple\">Germanium:</strong>Vi hm lng cao gp 5  8 ln so vi nhn sm gip tng cng h min dch, kch thch qu trnh tun hon mu, h tr iu tr v ngn nga kh nng ung th.</li>\r\n 	<li aria-level=\"1\"><strong data-cursor=\"-color-purple\">Triterpenes:</strong>C tc dng n nh huyt p, c ch s tin trin ca t bo ung th, h tr iu tr tiu ng, iu ha ni tit t.</li>\r\n 	<li aria-level=\"1\"><strong data-cursor=\"-color-purple\">Polysaccharide:</strong>Ngn chn s hnh thnh v pht trin ca cc gc t do trong c th, ngn cn s hnh thnh cc khi u, lm chm qu trnh lo ha.</li>\r\n 	<li aria-level=\"1\"><strong data-cursor=\"-color-purple\">Lingzhi-8 protein:</strong>iu tr hiu qu cc triu chng khi b men gan cao, vim gan, gan nhim m,; gii c gan v nng cao h min dch.</li>\r\n 	<li aria-level=\"1\"><strong data-cursor=\"-color-purple\">Adenosine:</strong>Thi c gan, iu ha cc c ch hot ng ca gan, tham gia vo qu trnh sinh ha ca c th, ci thin cht lng gic ng.</li>\r\n 	<li aria-level=\"1\"><strong data-cursor=\"-color-purple\">Cc vitamin v khong cht thit yu (Magie, Km, St, Canxi, ng,):</strong>Nng cao sc  khng, lm lnh cc tn thng trn c th.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-115 size-large\" src=\"http://localhost/wp_organic/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/nam-lim-xanh-quang-nam-3-1024x577.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"361\" />\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Nm lim xanh  Qung Nam cha nhiu dc cht qu v cc nguyn t vi lng tt cho sc khe (nh: Su tm)</p>\r\n<p data-cursor=\"-color-purple\">Tm li, tc dng ca nm lim xanh Qung Nam l h tr iu tr v ngn nga hiu qu nhng bnh l sau:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li aria-level=\"1\">Ung th</li>\r\n 	<li aria-level=\"1\">X gan, gan nhim m</li>\r\n 	<li aria-level=\"1\">Ph i tuyn tin lit</li>\r\n 	<li aria-level=\"1\">Tai bin mch mu no</li>\r\n 	<li aria-level=\"1\">Gout (cn gi l thng phong)</li>\r\n 	<li aria-level=\"1\">Vim khp</li>\r\n 	<li aria-level=\"1\">Tiu ng (cn gi l i tho ng)</li>\r\n 	<li aria-level=\"1\">au d dy, au i trng</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p data-cursor=\"-color-purple\">Ngoi ra, cng dng nm lim xanh Qung Nam cn gip phc hi, tng cng chc nng gan; tng cng sinh lc; gim m mu  ngn bo ph v chng tng cn; gim cao huyt p; gii c v thanh lc c th;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 data-cursor=\"-color-green\"><span id=\"13_cach_uong_nam_lim_xanh_hieu_qua_tot_cho_suc_khoe\" data-cursor=\"-color-green\">1.3. CCH UNG NM LIM XANH HIU QU, TT CHO SC KHE</span></h3>\r\n<p data-cursor=\"-color-purple\">Nm lim xanh  Qung Nam c th c s dng bng cch tn bt hoc thi lt ri hm tr  ung. Tuy nhin, khng phi ai cng bit cch ung nm lim xanh sao cho ng  pht huy c ti a cng dng ca loi tho dc ny.</p>\r\n<p data-cursor=\"-color-purple\"><img class=\"wp-image-116 size-large aligncenter\" src=\"http://localhost/wp_organic/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/nam-lim-xanh-quang-nam-4-1024x780.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"488\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\" data-cursor=\"-color-purple\">Ung nm lim xanh Qung Nam l cch s dng ph bin nht (nh: Su tm)</p>\r\n<p data-cursor=\"-color-purple\">Di y l hng dn cch ch bin nm lim xanh Qung Nam chun nht:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li aria-level=\"1\">Co, ct  loi b sch s ton b phn g lim cn bm li  trn thn v gc nm  trnh gy hi cho c th.</li>\r\n 	<li aria-level=\"1\">Ngm nm trong nc mui long khong 15 pht  lm mm nm v loi b hon ton cc c t cn st li.</li>\r\n 	<li aria-level=\"1\">Thi mng nm thnh tng lt v s dng u n hng ngy, vi hm lng khong 30  35g, nu vi 1,5  2 lt nc.</li>\r\n 	<li aria-level=\"1\">un nm trong nc cho n khi si th nh la, ri un tip 15 pht ri tt bp v  ngui. Bn c th ung trong ngy hoc bo qun trong ngn mt t lnh  ung dn nhng khng nn  qu 24 ting. Thi gian l tng nht l ung trc khi n sng.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p data-cursor=\"-color-purple\">Khi ung nm lim xanh c rt nhiu ngi thc mc rng liu Ung nm lim xanh nhiu c tt khng? hay Nn ung nm lim xanh trong thi gian bao lu?. Mc d l loi tho dc c tc dng tt cho sc khe v cha tng ghi nhn trng hp gp tc dng ph, nhng bn vn khng nn lm dng vic ung nm lim xanh v c th b ng c. Theo li khuyn ca cc chuyn gia, tt nht bn nn ung trong liu trnh 3 thng, sau  ngh 2 tun ri tip tc liu trnh mi.</p>\r\n<p data-cursor=\"-color-purple\"><img class=\"wp-image-117 size-full aligncenter\" src=\"http://localhost/wp_organic/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/nam-lim-xanh-quang-nam-5-1-e1689317010797.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"640\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\" data-cursor=\"-color-purple\">Khng nn lm dng vic s dng nm lim xanh  trnh b ng c (nh: Su tm)</p>\r\n<p data-cursor=\"-color-purple\">Ngoi ra, bn cn lu  rng khng phi tt c mi ngi u c th s dng c nm lim xanh. Sau y l danh sch nhng ngi khng nn ung nm lim xanh:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li aria-level=\"1\">Ngi b huyt p thp, v d gy tt huyt p.</li>\r\n 	<li aria-level=\"1\">Ngi b thn yu hoc c bnh l v thn.</li>\r\n 	<li aria-level=\"1\">Tr em di 2 tui.</li>\r\n 	<li aria-level=\"1\">Ph n mang thai.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p data-cursor=\"-color-purple\">Trong qu trnh s dng nm lim xanh Qung Nam, bn cng nn ch  mt s vn  nh:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li aria-level=\"1\">Khng s dng ni nhm  sc nc m ch dng ni gm, ni t hoc ni thy tinh.</li>\r\n 	<li aria-level=\"1\">Khng dng chung vi cc tho dc t nhin khc.</li>\r\n 	<li aria-level=\"1\">Tham kho  kin bc s ch