(150, 1, '2023-07-14 07:37:49', '2023-07-14 07:37:49', 'Hm lng dinh dng trong u c ve\r\n\r\n1. Protein Protein (hay cn c gi l m) l dng cht thit yu cho mt h min dch khe mnh, gip xy dng v ti to cc m ca c th. Theo khuyn ngh nhu cu dinh dng ca B Y t dnh cho ngi Vit Nam, mi ngy, trung bnh mt ngi trng thnh cn np 1,25g cht m/1 kg th trng. Thiu protein s khin tin trnh lo ha b y nhanh, da bn s xut hin nhiu np nhn, tc d gy rng, c th suy dinh dng v thng cm thy mt mi. u c ve cha protein thc vt cha hm lng cht bo thp, t cholesterol nn rt tt cho sc khe, c bit i vi nhng ngi ang c vn  v tim mch. Theo B Nng nghip Hoa K (USDA), trong 100g u c ve ti c cha 1,83g protein (7) v khi luc chn (khng cho mui) l 1,89g. (8)\r\n\r\n2. Vitamin C u c ve l mt ngun cung cp vitamin C di do. u c ve ti cha 12,2 mg vitamin C/100g v khi luc chn l 9,7 mg. Vitamin C l mt cht chng oxy ha, gip trung ha cc gc t do c th gy hi n cc t bo khe mnh v bo v cu trc DNA ca c th. Ngoi ra, vitamin C cn duy tr lng protein, cht bo v carbohydrate gip tng cng h min dch. Chng cng ng vai tr quan trng trong vic sn xut collagen, tng  n hi cho da, cng c xng v gn chc khe.\r\n\r\n3. Vitamin A Trn thc t, vitamin A khng phi l mt loi vitamin. Chng l mt nhm cc hp cht c gi l retinoid. Vitamin A ng vai tr quan trng trong vic tng cng th lc, h min dch v sc khe sinh sn. Hm lng vitamin A trong 100g u c ve ti l 690 IU v khi luc chn l 32 g, t hn 15% so vi hm lng c khuyn ngh np vo c th mi ngy.\r\n\r\n4. Vitamin K Nu c th thiu vitamin K, d bn c n nhiu thc phm cha canxi th xng vn khng th chc khe. Vitamin K cn thit cho qu trnh sn sinh protein gip xng hp th canxi d dng hn. Ngoi ra, chng cn gip duy tr mt  xng (BMD), gip bn gim nguy c mc bnh long xng. Theo khuyn ngh, mi ngy, ph n nn np 90 g vitamin K, cn nam gii cn n 120 g vitamin K. u c ve chn cha 47,9 g vitamin K/100g, cn u c ve ti cha 43 g vitamin K/100g.\r\n\r\n5. Cc loi vitamin khc Ngoi vitamin A, C v K, trong u c ve cn cha nhiu loi vitamin khc.\r\n\r\nHm lng cc loi vitamin trong 100g u ve ti:\r\n\r\nThiamin (vitamin B1) 0,082 mg\r\n\r\nRiboflavin (vitamin B2) 0,104 mg\r\n\r\nNiacin (vitamin B3) 0,734 mg\r\n\r\nVitamin B6 0,141 mg\r\n\r\nVitamin E 0,41 mg\r\n\r\nHm lng cc loi vitamin trong 100g u ve chn:\r\n\r\nThiamin 0,074 mg\r\n\r\nRiboflavin 0,097 mg\r\n\r\nNiacin 0,614 mg\r\n\r\nVitamin B6 0,056 mg\r\n\r\nVitamin E 0,46 mg\r\n\r\n6. Khong cht\r\n\r\nu c ve cha rt nhiu khong cht c li cho c th con ngi, c bit l mangan. Mangan c kh nng chng oxy ha tt. Ngoi ra, chng cn h tr qu trnh trao i cht trong c th, gip xng chc khe v thc y qu trnh lm lnh vt thng.\r\n\r\nHm lng khong cht trong 100g u ve ti:\r\n\r\nCanxi 37 mg St 1,03 mg\r\n\r\nMagie 25 mg\r\n\r\nPht pho 38 mg\r\n\r\nKali 211 mg\r\n\r\nNatri 6 mg\r\n\r\nKm 0,24 mg\r\n\r\nng 0,069 mg\r\n\r\nMangan 0,216 mg\r\n\r\nHm lng khong cht trong 100g u ve chn:\r\n\r\nCanxi 44 mg St 0.65 mg\r\n\r\nMagie 18 mg Photpho 29 mg\r\n\r\nKali 146 mg Natri 1 mg\r\n\r\nKm 0.25 mg\r\n\r\nng 0.057 mg\r\n\r\nMangan 0.285 mg\r\n\r\nu c ve khng ch lm gim nguy c mc cc bnh v tim mch, ngn nga ung th, bnh tiu ng m cn c li trong vic tng kh nng th thai  ph n. Tuy nhin, bn nn c ch  n hp l ch khng nn ch tp trung n u c ve. Ngoi ra, nu bn ang s dng cc loi thuc chng ng mu, hy xin thm  kin t bc s trong vic phn b u c ve vo khu phn n.', 'u Cove thng', 'u c ve (cn gi l u ty), tn khoa hc l Phaseolus vulgaris. u c ve thuc loi thn tho hng nm, c ngun gc t Trung M. Hin nay, u ve c trng ph bin khp th gii.  Vit Nam, u c ve c trng t Bc vo Nam, l mt trong nhng loi hoa mu c u tin gieo trng trong h thng lun canh vi la nc. Chng c chia lm hai nhm l u c ve leo v u c ve ln. Nhm u leo c trng theo dn, thng cho nng sut cao hn nhm u ln. L cy thuc loi l kp lng chim, mt l bng phng, hi nhm, c th n nh mt loi rau xanh. R thuc loi r cc, gm r chnh v nhiu r ph, c th dng lm thc n cho gia sc. Hoa u ve l hoa lng tnh, c nhiu mu nh trng ng, hng,  hoc tm. Hu ht cc ging u ny c qu di t 8  20 cm, rng t 0,6  1 cm. u nhn di, hnh kim v c mu xanh l nht hoc xanh l cy thm.', 'publish', 