(162, 1, '2023-07-14 07:48:15', '2023-07-14 07:48:15', 'C chua cherrykhng ch cha t calo v l ngun cung cp vitamin C v vitamin K di do, m c chua cherry cn c coi l thc phm c cht chng oxy ha cao v l mt trong nhng nguncung cp<strong>lycopene</strong>cao nht trong cc loi rau qu.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Lycopene c sc t mu , cng thc ha hc lC40H56, thuc h Carotenoid. Lycopene l mt cht chng oxy ha cc mnh c cho l thn dc ca tui xun, phng chng ung th v bnh tim mch. Ngy nay cc khoa hc  chng minh c tc dng c bit ca lycopen v kh nng ngn chn qu trnh oxi ha, lo ha t bo v chng gc t do.</li>\r\n 	<li>Lng lycopen c nhiu trn v c chua chn.</li>\r\n 	<li>Trong 100g c chua cha t 1-8g lycopene.</li>\r\n 	<li><em><strong>Theo NHS (S Y t Hoa K), mi ngy bn nn cung cp t 9-21mg lycopene cho c th,tng ng vic n 100-200gc chua cherry mi ngy.</strong></em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nNgoi vic cung cp lycopene, trong c chua cn c thnh phn dinh dng khc. Theo thng k, trong 123g c chua cherry c:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>22,1 calo</li>\r\n 	<li>4,8 gam carbs</li>\r\n 	<li>1,1 gam protein</li>\r\n 	<li>0,2 gam cht bo</li>\r\n 	<li>1,5 gam cht x</li>\r\n 	<li>15,6 miligam vitamin C (26%DV)</li>\r\n 	<li>1,025 n v quc t vitamin A (20%DV)</li>\r\n 	<li>9,7 microgam vitamin K (12%DV)</li>\r\n 	<li>292 miligam kali (8% DV)</li>\r\n 	<li>0,1 miligam mangan (7%DV)</li>\r\n 	<li>0,1 miligam vitamin B6 (5% DV)</li>\r\n 	<li>18,4 microgam folate (5% DV)\r\n*<strong><em>Note: %DV l vit tt ca tDaily Value)% Gi tr hng ngy.</em></strong>Gi tr ny do cc qun l Dc v thc phm Hoa K FDA  xut. N c thit k  gip ngi tiu dng xc nh mt thc phm/ 1 mn n cha bao nhiu lng cht dinh dng c th, da trn DRI (khu phn n tham kho) cho cht dinh dng . Cc con s % DV (c th hin trn nhn dinh dng) cho thy lng dng (quy c cho mt ngi c lng tiu th trung bnh 2.000 calo/ngy) v c trnh by nh l s phn trm trn tng s lng dng ca 1 ngy.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Thnh phn hp Cherry tomatoes mix bao gm:</strong>c chua cherry , c chua cherry vng, c chua cherry socola.\r\n<h2><strong>Cng dng c chua Cherry</strong></h2>\r\nC chua cherry c rt nhiu cc thnh phn dinh dng tt cho sc khe:\r\n\r\n<strong>Gim nguy c ung th:</strong>C chua cherry giu cht chng oxy ha nn s ngn nga v tiu dit cc gc t bo t do sinh ung th. Bn cnh , cc cht khng vim trong c chua cherry cn c nh gi cao trong vic phng cc bnh ung th d dy, ung th trc trng.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Cc nghin cu t nhng nm 1990 do Trng Y i hc Harvard thc hin cho thy nhng ngi n ng n nhiu c chua c nguy c pht trin ung th tuyn tin lit thp hn nhiu so vi nhng ngi khng n c chua. Mt s ngi n ng  n ti 10 phn c chua mi tun (hoc hn) - bao gm t cc ngun nh nc p c chua, nc st c chua v c chua sng. t nht nm nghin cu h tr gim 30% n 40% nguy c ung th tuyn tin lit lin quan n vic tiu th nhiu c chua hoc lycopene.</li>\r\n 	<li>Mt bo co ln c cng b bi Bnh vin Hong gia Victoria v i hc McGill ca Montreal  iu tra 11 nghin cu i chng v 10 nghin cu thun tp v vic s dng c chua, cc sn phm t c chua hoc lycopene  ngn nga ung th. Cc nh nghin cu pht hin ra rng c chua, c bit l khi n vi lng ln, c tc dng bo v ng k.</li>\r\n 	<li>Bn cnh lycopene, dinh dng c chua cha nhiu cht phytochemical mnh m khc c th gip chng li cc bnh mn tnh lan rng. V d, nghin cu cho thy rng cc axit phenolic c tm thy trong c chua c kh nng chng li ung th phi v kh nng c ch s hnh thnh cc hp cht nitrosamine trong c th.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Ci thin sc khe tim mch:</strong>C chua cherry c nh gi cao bi hiu qu vi bnh nhn mc bnh tim mch cng nh ngn nga cc bnh tim mch nguy him nh: au tim, x va ng mch, huyt p cao, t qu.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Cc lycopene trong c chua ngn chn qu trnh oxy ha lipid (m) trong huyt thanh, lm gim cc loi m mu c hi nh Triglyceride v cholesterol t trng thp (Low Density Lipoprotein cholesterol-LDL). Nhng loi m mu ny l nhng th phm chnh trong cc bnh tim mch do lm tng s lng ng cht bo trong cc mch mu, gy x va ng mch, tng huyt p</li>\r\n 	<li>Trong mt nghin cu nm 2002, nhng ngi trng thnh khe mnh ung lycopene di dng nc p c chua, nc st c chua v vin nang gel mm trong mt tun c pht hin c mc cholesterol b oxy ha LDL thp hn ng k so vi nhm i chng. Cc c ch c th c  c chua ci thin sc khe tim mch bao gm tng cng suy gim LDL, kch thc v thnh phn ht LDL, t tch t mng bm v thay i chc nng mch mu.</li>\r\n 	<li>Cc nh nghin cu hiu rng nhiu cht dinh dng c tm thy trong c chua mt phn hot ng ring l nhng cng hot ng cng nhau theo nhiu cch  bo v lipoprotein v t bo mch mu khi qu trnh oxy ha. V d, lutein c tm thy trong c chua cng c th gip ngn nga hoc lm chm s dy ln ca ng mch.</li>\r\n 	<li>Qu trnh oxy ha l l thuyt c chp nhn rng ri nht v s pht trin ca x va ng mch, hoc lm cng v dy cc ng mch c th dn n bnh tim mch. C chua cng l mt ngun cung cp kali di do v c th gip ngn nga cc vn  v huyt p do lng kali thp.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Tt cho mt:</strong>Vi lng vitamin A di do, c chua cherry l mt trong nhng la chn tt cho i mt khe. Bng vic b sung vitamin A thng qua n c chua cherry ni ring, bn s gim c nguy c c thy tinh th v thoi ha im vng, cung cp  m cho mt.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Mt hp cht bo v c gi l lutein c trong c chua v n rt tt cho mt ca bn. Lutein thng c nghin cu v sc khe ca mt v n bo v vng mc ca mt m chng ta cn  c th lc khe mnh. Vng mc c bit d b tn thng khi v gi do tc hi lu di ca bc x tia UV v stress oxy ha t cc yu t khc. Trong s nhiu carotenoid c trong c th, ch c lutein v zeaxanthin c tm thy trong phn ca mt, ni nh sng c thu knh hi t, c gi l im vng.</li>\r\n 	<li>Nghin cu cho thy lutein trong c chua c th hot ng ging nh mt phng php iu tr thoi ha im vng t nhin. Hy nh rng thoi ha im vng l nguyn nhn hng u gy m la  ngi ln tui. i vi nhng ngi khng c nguy c cao b thoi ha im vng, n c chua ch l mt cch tt  gip ci thin th lc v tin.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Tt cho da:</strong>Khi ni n vic chng li ung th da bng thc phm, c chua nn ng u danh sch ca bn. C chua l mt loi thc phm cung cp vitamin C tuyt vi, v vitamin C rt quan trng  gi cho kh nng min dch,  n hi, v ngoi v ln da ca ln da tr nn khe mnh khi c tui.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Mt iu cn lu  l vitamin C trong dinh dng c chua tp trung nhiu nht  cht dng gel bao quanh ht c chua. Hy cn thn ng  nc p qu gi ny chy ra qu nhiu v lng ph khi ct c chua.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Gip xng chc khe:</strong>Lycopene c lin quan n sc khe xng tt hn, c bit l  ngi cao tui.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Mt nghin cu iu tra tc ng ca ngun thc phm giu lycopene trong ch  n ca ph n ln tui cho thy nhng ngi thiu lng lycopene ng k c nguy c mc cc bnh lin quan n xng v c th b long xng cao hn. y l l do ti sao c chua v cc thc phm cha lycopene khc c khuyn khch nh mt phn ca ch  n ung chng lo ha, cha bnh. C chua cng l mt ngun cung cp cht dinh dng di do nh mangan, pht pho v vitamin K gip xy dng xng.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Gim cn khoa hc:</strong>Thc n gim cn khoa hc s khng th thiu c chua ni chung v c chua cherry ni ring. Trong c chua cherry c nhiu cht x, nc nn nhanh chng c cm gic no khi n, chuyn ha lng ng hiu qu, thc y qu trnh tiu hao m tha.\r\n\r\n<strong>Tt cho tiu ha:</strong>Cng vi cc loi rau, c, qu khc, c chua cherry rt giu cht x v nc nn nu n thng xuyn s gip bn trnh c nguy c to bn - nguyn nhn gy ra nhiu bnh v ng tiu ha nguy him.', 'C chua Cherry', 'C chua cherrythuc h bch anh, dng cy thn mm c th b trn mt t hoc leo cao. C chua cherry thng sng  nhng vng c kh hu mt m, l loi thc phm c s dng nhiu trong ch bin thc n hng ngy: lm salad, nu canh, xo hoc n sng trc tip, xay sinh t ung.', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'ca-chua-cherry', '', '', '2023-07-14 07:48:15', '2023-07-14 07:48:15', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wp_organic/?post_type=product&#038;p=162', 0, 'product', '', 0),
