(207, 1, '2023-07-14 14:19:51', '2023-07-14 14:19:51', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>5 thng u nm, xut khu go sang M tng trng 71,3%, mc tng mnh nht trong cc quc gia nhp go Vit.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Theo B Nng nghip v Pht trin Nng thn, khi lng go xut khu 6 thng u nm t 3,52 triu tn v 1,72 t USD, tng ng tng 16,2% v khi lng v 4,6% v gi tr.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Philippines vn l th trng tiu th go ln nht ca Vit Nam trong 5 thng u nm vi 43,6% th phn. Xut khu go sang th trng ny trong 5 thng t 1,27 triu tn v hn 589 triu USD, tng 34,8% v khi lng v 17,7% v gi tr so vi cng k nm ngoi.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Cng vi Philippines, M l th trng ngy cng chung go Vit. c bit, trong 5 thng u nm, lng go xut sang quc gia ny tng 71,3%, mc tng cao nht trong s cc nc nhp khu go ca Vit Nam. Theo B Nng nghip M  USDA, th trng ny rt a chung cc loi go thm, ht di nh ST25 ca Vit Nam. y l loi go  nhp khu vo M gn 2 nm nay.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Tng t, EU cng l khu vc gia tng nhp cc loi go cht lng cao ca Vit Nam. Trong thng 6, ln u tin, 500 tn go mang thng hiu Cm Vit Nam Rice ca Lc Tri  c xut sang c, H Lan v Php. Ti Php, thng hiu trn ca Lc Tri c by bn ti Carrefour  h thng i siu th ln nht chu u.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":208,\"width\":838,\"height\":558,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-resized\"><img src=\"http://localhost/wp_organic/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/nong-dan-xa-thanh-an.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-208\" width=\"838\" height=\"558\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Mc d ang c th trng M, chu u a chung, go Vit vn ng trc nhiu thch thc&nbsp;khi i th l Thi Lan, n  ang bn go vi gi r do ng tin nc ny gim mnh.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>C th go tiu chun 5% tm ca Thi Lan  mc 420-425 USD mt tn, gim 25 USD so vi thng trc. Ti n , go 5% tm  mc 355-360 USD mt tn, gim 2 USD so vi u thng. ng rupee chm mc thp k lc lm tng li nhun ca cc nh xut khu t doanh s bn hng  nc ngoi. c bit l loi go tm ca n , xut khu ang rt tt do gi c cnh tranh hn i th. Lnh cm bt ng ca n  i vi xut khu la m vo thng trc  khin cc nh bun go tng cng mua v t cc n t hng bt thng cho cc t giao hng lu hn, do lo ngi s b hn ch.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Hin go 5% tm ca Vit Nam  mc 418-423 USD mt tn, tng 3 USD so vi thng trc. Ngun cung ang tng nhng theo Cc Ch bin v Pht trin Th trng Nng sn, nhu cu tiu th c xu hng gim.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Hip hi Lng thc Vit Nam (VFA) d bo, d th trng nhp khu bin ng v cnh tranh mnh m, xut khu go ca Vit Nam trong nm nay c t 6-6,2 triu tn, tng ng nm 2020 v 2021 vi tr gi trn 3,2 t USD.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Theo B Nng nghip v Pht trin Nng thn, xut khu go trong nm nay s duy tr th hng tt do ngnh la go Vit Nam ngy cng c ci thin v cht lng. Ngnh hng ny tip tc l tr ct  gip ngnh nng nghip t mc tiu cn ch kim ngch xut khu trn 50 t USD.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Xut khu go sang M tng vt', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '__trashed', '', '', '2023-07-14 14:20:50', '2023-07-14 14:20:50', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wp_organic/?p=207', 0, 'post', '', 0),
