(212, 1, '2023-07-14 14:22:17', '2023-07-14 14:22:17', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Theo phng vin TTXVN ti Tokyo, ngy 30/6, ti th  Tokyo, Cng ty C phn Tp on Tn Long  phi hp vi Ngn hng Kiraboshi t chc l ra mt sn phm go ST25 mang thng hiu A An m cng ty  a thnh cng vo th trng Nht Bn.</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Pht biu ti s kin, i s Vit Nam ti Nht Bn V Hng Nam nh gi cao n lc ca Ngn hng Kiraboshi v Tp on Tn Long trong vic a sn phm go cht lng cao ST25 vo mt th trng c tiu chun cao nh Nht Bn.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>i s ni: Vit Nam l mt trong nhng nc xut khu go hng u th gii. Go Vit Nam  c mt  hn 100 th trng trn th gii. Tuy nhin, y l ln u tin go ST25 ca Vit Nam c mt ti th trng Nht Bn. Vic xut khu go ST25 sang th trng Nht Bn l mt minh chng cho thy Vit Nam khng ch xut khu go nhiu m cn xut khu go ngon, p ng c cc tiu chun rt cao ca th trng Nht Bn.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Nhn dp ny, i s by t hy vng ngi tiu dng Nht Bn s n nhn go ST25 v c thm nhiu sn phm go Vit Nam s thm nhp thnh cng vo th trng ny.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>V phn mnh, ng Nguyn Chnh Trung, Ph Tng Gim c Cng ty C phn Tp on Tn Long, cho bit cng ty  bt u tp trung vo vic sn xut go  ng bng sng Cu Long t nm 2017, vi m hnh bao tiu la canh tc trc tip t nng dn. ng Trung khng nh: Vic hp tc gia doanh nghip v ngi nng dn  mang li sn phm go sch,  tiu chun xut sang Nht Bn. iu ny khng ch gp phn nng cao gi tr ca sn phm m cn gip tng thu nhp cho ngi nng dn.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Tr li phng vn TTXVN bn l s kin, i s V Hng Nam ni:  a c go ST25 vo th trng Nht Bn, chng ta phi vt qua hn 600 tiu chun k thut. 600 tiu chun k thut l mt yu cu rt kht khe, cng vo  l s kh tnh ca ngi tiu dng Nht Bn. V vy, ti cho rng y l mt thnh cng rt ln ca ngi sn xut cng nh cc nh thng mi  a c go ST25 vo th trng Nht Bn.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Theo ng Nguyn Chnh Trung, cng ty  a th trng Nht Bn vo k hoch xut khu cch y 1 nm khi ln u tin cho ra mt go ST25 ti th trng ni a. ng cho bit: Khi tham gia vo th trng Nht Bn, chng ti khng t mc tiu v s lng m mun tip cn cc i tng khch hng c th v la chn i tc thng mi phn phi bn l c uy tn.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Theo Tp on Tn Long, ti th trng Nht Bn, sn phm go ST25 mang thng hiu A An s c nhp khu bi Cng ty Suntomi International v sau  s c Cng ty Spice House phn phi trong cc siu th v ca hng.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>ng Khorow Hassanzadeh, Ch tch Cng ty TNHH Spice House  n v phn phi go ST25  Nht Bn, cho bit go ST25  tng t danh hiu Go ngon nht th gii vo nm 2019 v c nhiu ngi tin dng. V vy, Spice House  phi hp vi Ngn hng Kiraboshi v cng ty nhp khu  a sn phm ny ti ngi tiu dng Nht Bn. Spice House  a go ST25 ra by bn  mt s ca hng cch y 3 tun v cho n nay  tiu th c 8 tn.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Theo Thng v Vit Nam ti Nht Bn, ln gn y nht go Vit Nam trng thu xut khu sang Nht Bn l nm 2012. Sau , go Vit Nam b pht hin d lng thuc bo v thc vt vt mc cho php nn khng c cc cng ty Nht Bn a vo danh sch tham gia u thu na. V vy, k t  n nay, go Vit Nam xut khu vo th trng Nht Bn ch yu qua ng phi mu dch vi s lng khng ng k v ch yu c dng ch bin thc phm.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>S liu thng k ca Hi quan Nht Bn cho thy nm ngoi, kim ngch xut khu go ca Vit Nam sang Nht Bn ch t 48,7 triu yen, tng 73% so vi nm 2020 nhng ch chim khong 0,09% trong tng kim ngch nhp khu go ca Nht Bn.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Go ST25 ca Vit Nam  thm nhp vo th trng Nht Bn', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'gao-st25-cua-viet-nam-da-tham-nhap-vao-thi-truong-nhat-ban', '', '', '2023-07-14 14:22:19', '2023-07-14 14:22:19', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wp_organic/?p=212', 0, 'post', '', 0),
