(215, 1, '2023-07-14 14:23:17', '2023-07-14 14:23:17', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Ngy 8-7, ti An Giang, B Nng nghip v pht trin nng thn t chc hi ngh S kt sn xut trng trt v h thu 2022, trin khai k hoch sn xut v thu ng, v ma nm 2022 ti Nam B v ng bng sng Cu Long.</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>V h thu 2022, tng din tch xung ging ton vng Nam B l trn 1,5 triu hecta, gim 20.000 ha so vi v h thu 2021; nng sut c t 5,7 tn/ha, tng 0,06 tn/ha; sn lng c t 9 triu tn, gim 13.000 tn so vi v h thu 2021.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Ring vng ng bng sng Cu Long xung ging trn 1,49 triu ha, gim 16.000ha; nng sut c t 5,7 tn/ha. Cn vng ng Nam B xung ging 82.000ha, gim 3.600ha; nng sut c t 5,6 tn/ha, tng 0,2 tn/ha; sn lng t 465.000 tn.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>V thu ng 2022, vng ng bng sng Cu Long gieo s 700.000ha, gim 3.500ha; nng sut 5,7 tn/ha, tng 0,05 tn/ha; sn lng 4,0 triu tn, tng 17.000 tn so vi thu ng 2021.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Theo Trung tm D bo kh tng thy vn quc gia, nh l chnh v nm 2022 c kh nng xut hin vo gia thng 10, mc nc nh l ti Tn Chu dao ng  mc 3,5  3,7m (xp x v trn mc bo ng 1 t 0,1  0,2m, thp hn nh l trung bnh nhiu nm khong 0,2  0,4m, cao hn cng k nm 2021 khong 0,7  0,9m), mc nc nh l ti Chu c dao ng  mc 3  3,2m (xp x v trn mc bo ng 1 t 0,1  0,2m, thp hn trung bnh nhiu nm khong 0,3  0,5m, cao hn cng k nm 2021 khong 0,4  0,6m). Nhn chung, nh l nm 2022  mc xp x v cao hn mc bo ng 1, thp hn trung bnh nhiu nm, nhng cao hn nm 2021.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>B H Th Ngc Lan  ph gim c S Nng nghip v pht trin nng thn tnh Long An  cho bit n thi im ny Long An c hng ngn hecta gim trong v h thu l do ngi dn b la. V gi vt t nng nghip tng cao do nh hng ca bo gi, c bit l phn bn vt t nng nghip nn nng dn Long An  gim din tch trng la hn 4.000ha.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Mc d chng ti t k hoch h thu 2022 nhng so vi cng k 2021 th din tch la ti Long An gim. Nguyn nhn chnh do ngi dn trng la khng c li nhun (nht l ngi trng la thu)  tr t cho ch rung. Ti kin ngh b v cc tnh thnh phi bt tay x l nghim tnh trng phn bn gi lng hnh gn y gy bc xc d lun, b Lan ni.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Pht biu kt lun hi ngh, Th trng B Nng nghip v pht trin nng thn L Quc Doanh khng nh gi phn bn hin nay rt cao  nh hng rt ln n sn xut nng nghip. Tuy nhin, b con nng dn  gim c phn bn, thuc rt nhiu  gim chi ph sn xut rt ln nn t su bnh, t phun thuc hn.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Nh gim chi ph kp thi m nng dn trong v ny chc chn c chi ph rt thp hn so vi cc nm trc. Do , cc a phng phi y mnh cng tc tuyn truyn, vn ng ngi dn hn ch s dng phn, thuc  tit kim sn xut hiu qu hn.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Theo cc ngnh, nm 2022 nay l s khng ln, ch cao hn bo ng 1 m thi. Tc l dao ng chng 3,7m ti Tn Chu. Tuy nhin chng ta khng c ch quan, nht l cc a phng ven bin: C Mau, Sc Trng, Bc Liu, Th trng L Quc Doanh nhn nh.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Nng dn b la hng ngn hecta v gi phn bn, vt t qu cao', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'nong-dan-bo-lua-hang-ngan-hecta-vi-gia-phan-bon-vat-tu-qua-cao', '', '', '2023-07-14 14:23:19', '2023-07-14 14:23:19', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wp_organic/?p=215', 0, 'post', '', 0),
