(218, 1, '2023-07-14 14:24:14', '2023-07-14 14:24:14', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Chnh sch Zero COVID ca Trung Quc khin cho xut khu (XK) thy sn sang th trng ny gp nhiu ch tc. Tuy nhin, do sn xut b nh tr nn th trng ny cng thiu ht ngun cung, nhu cu nhp khu thy sn ca Trung Quc gia tng, thu ht nhiu doanh nghip Vit Nam XK sang th trng t dn ny.</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Theo Hip hi Ch bin v Xut khu thy sn Vit Nam (VASEP), XK thy sn sang Trung Quc tt c 5 thng u nm nay u tng trng t hai n ba con s so vi cng k nm trc. Trong , thng 2 tng ti 138%, thng 4 tng 113%.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Tng 5 thng u nm 2022, XK thy sn Vit Nam sang Trung Quc t 771 triu USD, tng 91% so vi cng k nm 2021. Trong , hai sn phm chim t trng chi phi l c tra (48%) v tm (35%).</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Ring mt hng c tra mang v 371 triu USD, tng 124% so vi cng k nm trc. Trong , sn phm c tra phi-l, ct khc t 297 triu USD; c tra nguyn con t gn 74 triu USD.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>i vi tm, XK tm hm tng t ph vi mc tng gp gn 29 ln so vi cng k nm trc khi t trn 108 triu USD, cao gn bng kim ngch XK tm chn trng (119 triu USD, tng 61%); trong khi XK tm s gim 9% (t 43 triu USD).</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Ngoi 2 sn phm ch lc trn, a s cc loi hi sn XK sang Trung Quc st gim so vi cng k nm trc (c ng gim 60%; cc loi c bin gim 9%; ch c v surimi gim 25%).</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Tuy nhin, v nhiu nh my ti Trung Quc b ng ca, sn xut b nh tr, nn th trng ny cng thiu ht ngun cung thy sn cho tiu th ni a v ch bin XK. Do vy, nhu cu nhp khu thy sn ca Trung Quc ang gia tng, thu ht nhiu hn s doanh nghip Vit Nam XK sang th trng ny bt chp nhng thch thc trn.Theo VASEP, COVID-19 bng pht mnh v thi  kin nh vi chnh sch Zero COVID ca chnh quyn Trung Quc khin cho XK thy sn sang th trng ny gp nhiu ch tc khi nhiu cng nhp khu b ng ca v vic kim tra COVID trn hng ng lnh ngy cng kht khe.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>V xu hng, th trng Trung Quc tip tc b chi phi bi dch COVID khin nhp khu thy sn b nh hng. Tuy nhin, v di hn, thy sn nhp khu ca Trung Quc s tip tc tng trng. Trong , loi thy sn ph bin l tm s c tiu th nhiu hn trong cc h gia nh (ngun cung tm t Trung Quc gim trong 3 nm qua do nh hng ca i dch COVID-19). Cc loi thy sn nhp khu m ngi tiu dng Trung Quc a thch v c khi lng nhp khu ln l tm, c h, mc ng, c tra, c hi</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Kim ngch XK thy sn Vit Nam 5 thng u nm 2022 t hn 4,7 t USD, tng 44,2% so vi cng k nm 2021. Trong , dn u l mt hng tm vi hn 1,8 t USD (tng hn 41%); c tra t hn 1,2 t USD (tng gn 90%); c ng hn 462 triu USD (tng hn 58%).</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>D bo XK thy sn c nm 2022 s t 10 t USD, tng 12% so vi nm 2021. Trong , XK tm t 4,2 t USD; c tra 2,5-2,6 t USD; c ng gn 1 t USD; mc, bch tuc khong 650 triu USD; cn li cc hi sn khc khong 1,6 t USD.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Xut khu thu sn sang Trung Quc tng gn gp i nm 2021', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'xuat-khau-thuy-san-sang-trung-quoc-tang-gan-gap-doi-nam-2021', '', '', '2023-07-14 14:24:15', '2023-07-14 14:24:15', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wp_organic/?p=218', 0, 'post', '', 0),
